      "rule_text": "The gradient background palette is a closed, approved set: Brand Blue → Dark Navy (#00529b → #011E45) for dark backgrounds and blue masthead/waves; Sky Blue → Deep Blue (#358CCB → #003D74) for blue backgrounds/waves; Sunshine → 75% Gold for warm backgrounds; Golden Sand → White → Light Blue (#FEF1C8 → #ffffff → #E6F0F9) for soft light backgrounds; and Golden Sand → 75% Gold → Sunshine for warm light-to-saturated backgrounds. Never invent new gradients — only use these approved combinations as section backgrounds, optionally paired with the wave graphic or the LISRAYA logo mark.",
